                     <interp inst="t18150111-122-person1034" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a watch-maker; I purchased this spoon of the prisoner's mother; I gave eight shillings for it.</p>
               <p>GUILTY, aged 12.</p>
